{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d58b53219f","title":"对右派分子施世雕的辩论记录","origin":"根据网络材料打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c5614e476","index":0,"year":1958,"month":1,"day":31,"articleId":"d58b53219f"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"47bec1ad48","name":"施世雕"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cedb284f8d","type":"title","text":"对右派分子施世雕的辩论记录","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"8d74880bb2","type":"authors","text":"施世雕","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"c6454fd450","type":"paragraph","text":"【施世雕，浙江人，曾为中国人民解放军第二十一军六十二师某营军官，抗美援朝时期入朝作战，该部1955年春季回国，他同时转业到地方，工作单位应该为山东省济宁市的公安部门的劳改农场，最迟至1958年初被划为右派，最后具体处理结果未详。在对他的批判辩论中，施世雕面对已经无法更改的右派分子的结论，坚持为自己辩护】","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"c1925496c3","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞的发言：施世雕自大鸣大放以来睡到九点才起床，为什么应作交代？在大字报上恶毒的反对粮食统购统销政策。施世雕睁着眼睛说瞎话，这与他的本质有关系。他不承认社会主义，他反对社会主义制度，他用心理来攻击社会主义。他竭尽心机的来攻击我们。从他的“控告信”里可以看出他早已站到了美国方面。当我写出了反驳“饿浮载道”的大字报后，他说我驴唇不对马嘴，当然施世雕的嘴不能对上我的目的，他说我们由于粮食统购统销造成了饿浮载道，可是我们究竟饿死了多少人？应作交代。他对我们部队的专业政策不满进行诬蔑说：“生了小孩卡死也不叫他当兵啦”“美国鬼子打到家门口也不管啦”，当然他是不管的，而且他还欢迎的。他参加工作根本不是为了革命，自转业后二年多没工作就可以想像啦。施世雕的人生观是资产阶级的人生观，他的主义是无政府主义，施世雕吃人民的饭不给人民工作，反而印反动传单企图分发。他前几天要求回家，赵科长没允许，他说是阴谋，我们不能放走反革命，你才是阴谋因为你企图逃脱。我们要叫施世雕交待历史，施世雕是反革命家属，施世雕的本质是反动的，我们不能认为他有精神病，他的反党反社会主义是有纲领有目的，他说右派分子不是反革命分子，他曲解浙江省委书记的报告，施世雕的反党反社会主义的目的纲领应当交待。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"a5bfc191bb","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕的交待：李明瑞的发言是这个富农分子的报复，不符合事实。右派分子就是反革命分子这个说法就是您的谬论。我认为右派分子不是反革命分子，文件上根本没将右派分子和反革命分子列在一起。我国自一九五六年来经过了三大运动：农业合作化、公私合营、知识分子的改造之后，阶级斗争基本上消除啦，转向了人民内部矛盾，资产阶级有他积极的方面有他落后的方面，我们一方面改造他落后的方面，另一方面利用他积极的方面。现在说右派分子是向党进攻但是我们有强的力量，这一小撮右派分子，我们不是用过去的方法，我们用讲道理摆事实的办法，右派分子没什么武器，所要改造他的思想，右派分子是反革命分子这个论点我认为是不正确的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"bd48248185","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨的发言：右派分子施世雕说右派分子不是反革命，他说他找来很多文件没有这种说法，资产阶级有两面性是对的，但资产阶级的右派分子就是他本身没有一点进步性，他们想推翻社会主义叫资产阶级复辟，他反对的死社会主义，我们建设的是社会主义，他们不是反革命是什么？就你本身说，你早就是混入革命的敌人，他在部队的时候他就处心积虑的收集反对党的材料，他写了“控告”中央的信偷着印了四十多份企图散发。美帝国主义的心理作战也就是这样，他和美帝国主义的心理作战一样的，这就看出已经构成了一系列的反革命活动，就是社会上的反革命所说的话也不必他的恶毒。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"03c0952d3c","type":"appellation","text":"施世雕说：右派分子是反动派但不一定是反革命分子。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"2f47cdf971","type":"paragraph","text":"徐绍锡同志说：我国第一阶段的革命是什么？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d552e84e17","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕答：是旧民主主义革命。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e79058946b","type":"paragraph","text":"又问：第二阶段的革命是什么？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"06b5cd8f64","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是新民主主义革命。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"956afae59c","type":"paragraph","text":"又问：现在是什么革命？敌人是谁？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"6c0ed268d9","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是社会主义革命，敌人是资产阶级反革命。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"01d5d41cfd","type":"paragraph","text":"楮度铎问：反革命和右派分子有什么区别？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5ccef5d4dd","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕答：反革命有一定的反革命活动，右派分子没什么活动。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e26ce06006","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：施世雕在名词上给我们纠缠，国民党反动派的一分子是什么分子？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"db3077d4fd","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：文件是指思想上讲的，我认为反革命分子有行动有破坏活动。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"a5feb98eef","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：反革命分子有了行动以后才算反革命吗？什么叫行动？","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"12ee4f70cf","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：反革命分子有行动破坏我们的革命，右派分子主要是思想反动。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"703343c705","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：给杜近芳写信是什么意思？你和他有什么亲戚？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"920ec302c8","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我从济南回来以后我觉得脑子里轰轰的，是他们用机器专门刺激我的，我在戏报上看到的杜近芳的名字。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"351ab041af","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你这封信是拥护党还是反对党？","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"bd6088dbcd","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我是拥护党的，党有缺点错误我应该批判吗？","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"47356e17f8","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：党恶毒在哪里？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"f0d8821d76","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：它用机器折磨我是不应该的。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"9bc26038eb","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：机器在哪里？","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"63fe5acd9c","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：在脑子里。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d30eacecac","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：什么是法西斯？","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"13d68ff16b","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：他用机器毒害人，法西斯是最不人道的。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5a85ce1c03","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：蒋介石是谁打垮的？","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"24e356f063","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这个大家都知道。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"842b0a4f78","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：谁领导的打倒了美帝国主义？","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"740d7bc294","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这个都知道。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"494ee6bd0a","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：人民有选举权吗？","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"48f8c1dddb","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：有。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"72032b41bb","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：过去有没有选举权？","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"93ce2f2acd","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：不清楚。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"a5ae973329","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：在部队里有自由吗？","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d407e10412","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：有。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"0b79a2f9b5","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：在部队里是法西斯教育吗？","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"905863149f","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我没有讲。是在一九五六年二月份以后头脑里有了苏联武器以后是法西斯教育。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"f28314dfd9","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：粮食统购统销五五年是不是糟的很？","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"92f5dbe5bd","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我认为缺点是很大的，老百姓应买粮食买不到，可以找报纸看。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"27600b6206","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：“饿浮载道”是你讲的吗？什么意思。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"b4aeec76ce","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这是我的粗枝大叶。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"93a3c85b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：广西事件为什么拿到粮食政策上来比呢？","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e062896830","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这个我应作检讨。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"ae78d306fd","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：济宁地区受水灾以后国家购粮他们的粮食没有？","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5141a69bff","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：没有。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"eac72f5a10","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你为什么说是统购统销问题。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"06cae331ca","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我没说统购统销问题。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"16b6c1d8a5","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你说邹县55年饿死多少人？","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"aea04fbd88","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：五五年那个情况是很严重的，我没见有饿死的。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"711ea33cc2","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你为什么说饿死很多人？","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"b9ef1c4a15","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我写的过份了一点，这是我的 。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"1089a10682","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你写的其他的大字报有粗枝大叶吗？","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"8e7d95bd3c","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：很难说。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"10fea06a9e","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你说饿浮载道形容的不算过份也是粗枝大叶吗？中国这么个大国要是饿浮载道得死多少人？","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"cdb54e694f","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我不是说全国。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"11a92d5129","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：五五年老百姓是吃树叶吗？","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"4ae8a0823a","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我的家庭就就是这样。反问：你为什么钻空子？","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"336cbac75b","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你大字报上为什么说是全国差不多都是这样？","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"93ed8cbd99","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：可能是这样。","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5aab0606b0","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：邹县有没有饿浮载道？","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"270910978a","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：没有。我也不能肯定。","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"13a8a4a2ed","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：没有实施的事说是有这个事是不是造谣？","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"2e695837f9","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：那个情况不是这样。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"995e346c96","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你对问题的看法是唯物的还是唯心的？","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"498fc83881","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：是唯物的。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"3121fa1dc0","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：这里没有饿死人说饿死人啦怎么解释？","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"f6a38dfcca","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：可以推算。是否是事实我没实地调查，这是我形容过度，是不对的。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"a50276970c","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你见到饿死人了吗？","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"fc43124fba","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我没见到，听人家说的。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5484ea8f43","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：听谁说的？","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"191b3234ae","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我没记下来。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"18be24a9a1","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你说到底死了多少人？","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e82a5c022e","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我形容统购统销的紧张情况。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"3f8b2da51f","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：如果别人说是饿浮载道你怎么说？","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d25011ddce","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：现在是整风和平时不同。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"35d869a6f4","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：因为整风就可以乱说吗？","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d765c1ede5","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这个饿浮载道的实际意义我没有领会到。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"73c91bb49a","type":"paragraph","text":"赵佩科长：你说是否需要统购统销政策？","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"58564788bd","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：需要。","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"f3ae756ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"赵科长：你怎么说要中央检查“饿浮载道”是不是粮食统购统销的结果？","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"be9baf6fd7","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我不是这样说的。","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"262779308b","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：讨饭的街头巷尾，是否是事实？","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"928c73226c","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我没说到处都是。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5d3ee820b2","type":"paragraph","text":"赵科长：你是文法上的毛病还是向党进攻？（施未答）","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"b0ffa956c5","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：你家里是否吃树皮啦？","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"f5d2a736c3","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我没见，家里来信说的。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d0ef091035","type":"paragraph","text":"刘兴汉：我家也是浙江从来没听说过吃树皮树叶。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"ff5323fca6","type":"paragraph","text":"林德才：我家也是浙江，我们家里从来也未吃过树皮树叶子。解放前后都未吃过，也没饿死过人，解放前饿死过人，55年下半年我也回到家去过。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"be68f14f5b","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：你可以到我家去调查，你（指林德才）上我家去了吗？","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"4c9611a153","type":"paragraph","text":"林德才：反党反社会主义是什么？","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"22231850d4","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕： 五六年前可以说是反革命分子，五六年以后变啦，把他划到资产阶级右派分子，反党反社会主义的他没有行动。","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"7372a5eeb7","type":"paragraph","text":"林德才：你散布反动传单，是不是反对共产党？","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e7181c3b77","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：因为共产党用机器迫害我。","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"105655ca0b","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：是不是由于右派分子多就不算反革命啦？","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"c81cf11550","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：对右派分子斗争主要是思想上的斗争，他要是现行犯活动的话，就把他算反革命。","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"8c235d5d6e","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：造谣是不是现行活动？","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"a601cb7c2c","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我不是造谣，这是整风，您能驳倒我的话我可以检讨。","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5d38d9212d","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：你见到了“饿浮载道”吗？","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"129a85b745","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：没见到，我是形容，造谣也分有意、无意的。","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"eb6284f5e7","type":"paragraph","text":"刘兴汉：没有根据的形容算什么？","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"df5cbc33cb","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我是用词错啦。","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"78cc708ac9","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：你写大字报的目的是什么？","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e703fd764f","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：帮助党整风。","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"08e8b7d6d9","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：没有的事你怎么帮助党整风？什么目的？","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"6bd3e01e08","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这个错啦。我没有目的。反问：“你说粮食统购统销开始是不是有紧张情况？”","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"7ddbeadc3a","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：你为什么不讲理呢？你即是知识分子，如果有人说你杀人啦，你说手不当家能算理吗？","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"eafc9803f9","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我用词不当。并反问：“你是不是没写错过呢？”","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5e3a2d9c56","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：你错的根源是什么？怎样产生的错误思想呢？","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"b94bb64b8d","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：糊糊涂涂写的，我当时写的时候是形容有很多讨饭的。","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d093b0483f","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：统购统销有好多方面吗？","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"7f3c98188c","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：好的方面很多。","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e8c3971003","type":"paragraph","text":"洪烨：大字报上你没写一张好事，邹县没有的事你写出来啦！什么动机？能说没思想吗？（施未答）","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"3009ed8ea5","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：你是不是帮助党整风？为什么不讲事实？","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"deebc06d36","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我本意是帮助党整风，就是用词错啦。","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"c9f8f53510","type":"paragraph","text":"李明瑞：这个“万恶的共产党”是谁写的？","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e54e9e24b6","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：这是我脑子里的机器。","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"8471b25737","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：什么机器？","index":120,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"0e978cb339","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：苏联的机器。","index":121,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"e292cba185","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：那个“控告书”是谁写的？","index":122,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"3d16700e2f","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：是通过我的手。","index":123,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"d55b0ea6ad","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：谁支配你的手写的？","index":124,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"31f7f44d8b","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：苏联武器。","index":125,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"ca98e56965","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：你为什么单说共产党的坏呢？","index":126,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"5edf9fdb9b","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：是苏联武器迫害的我。","index":127,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"c9879f1892","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：共产党每月给你五十多块钱你怎么不说共产党的好呢？国民党、美帝国主义给你钱花了吗？","index":128,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"49e03378ca","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：我早就不想花这五十多块钱了。","index":129,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"ec80386fea","type":"paragraph","text":"李殿荣：你怎么不讲理呢？","index":130,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"},{"id":"a0e6c20d28","type":"paragraph","text":"施世雕：您用枪杀我也随您的便，我认为您不讲理。","index":131,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f"}],"page":{"id":"6ea7840b41","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d58b53219f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}